# DeepFake Detection — Next-Level Upgrade Plan

## Overview

The existing project has a solid Flask + PyTorch backend (`Main_deepfake.py`) with a ResNeXt50 + LSTM model. The frontend is currently a compiled React bundle (static files) passed through Flask's `render_template`. The plan is to **replace the old React bundle frontend** with a fully custom, stunning HTML/CSS/JS page served directly by Flask, while also upgrading the backend with better performance, error handling, and additional response data.

---

